'''大英帝国与英联邦博物馆'''（{{lang-en|British Empire and Commonwealth Museum}}）是[[英国|英国]][[布里斯托尔|布里斯托尔]]博物馆，旨在探索[[大英帝国|大英帝国]]历史和英国殖民统治对世界其他地区的影响。该博物馆于2002年开放，2013年进入自愿清算阶段。

==博物馆==
2002年，博物馆在建于1840年的[[布里斯托尔圣殿草地站|布里斯托尔圣殿草地站]]开放，由[[伊桑巴德·金德姆·布鲁内尔|伊桑巴德·金德姆·布鲁内尔]]设计，翻新和改造耗资800万英镑。<ref name="museumsassociation-20110316" />它长达{{convert|220|ft|m|abbr=on|adj=mid}}，铁木屋顶跨度为{{convert|72|ft|m|abbr=on}}。这座Ⅰ级[[登录建筑|登录建筑]]<ref>{{cite web | title=Bristol Old Station, Temple Meads | work=historicengland.org.uk | url=https://historicengland.org.uk/listing/the-list/list-entry/1209622 | accessdate=2007-03-13 | archive-date=2021-01-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210115215047/https://historicengland.org.uk/listing/the-list/list-entry/1209622 | dead-url=no }}</ref>已成爲[[世界遗产|世界遗产]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.english-heritage.org.uk/server/show/conGap.6 |title=British Empire and Commonwealth Museum |accessdate=2007-03-13 |work=English Heritage |archive-date=2020-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101005631/https://www.english-heritage.org.uk/server/show/conGap.6 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

博物馆有一个繁荣的出版部门，出版殖民时代生活的书籍，如[[北罗得西亚|北罗得西亚]]警察的历史，[[英国东印度公司|英国东印度公司]]和东印度军队。博物馆还收藏了英联邦学会的文物；大量的照片、纸张、电影和[[口述历史|口述历史]]档案，和服装收藏。这些现在由布里斯托尔博物馆、画廊和档案馆照管。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://museums.bristol.gov.uk/narratives.php?irn=8786|title=Bristol Museums Galleries Archives – British Empire and Commonwealth|access-date=2019-06-06|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126055637/http://museums.bristol.gov.uk/narratives.php?irn=8786|dead-url=no}}</ref>

博物馆还有新世界[[壁毯|壁毯]]<ref name="Tapestry to Bristol">{{cite news |url= http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/bristol/somerset/3165712.stm |title= World's biggest tapestry on move |publisher= [[BBC_News|BBC News]] |date= 2003-10-05 |quote= Now the 39 million stitch tapestry, which was 23 years in the making. |accessdate= 2020-12-29 |archive-date= 2019-03-06 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190306045303/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/bristol/somerset/3165712.stm |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="Pow Wow">{{cite web |url=http://www.dayoutwiththekids.co.uk/event.php?id=288 |title=British Empire and Commonwealth Museum Bristol: Pow Wow – Special exhibition until 1st November 2006 |quote=Pow Wow also features the stunning New World Tapestry. Created over 25 years in England's West Country and larger than the Bayeaux Tapestry, it presents a light-hearted history of the colonial period as well as providing a fascinating record of the people and plants that made possible Britain's first empire in America. |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070504230202/http://www.dayoutwiththekids.co.uk/event.php?id=288 |archivedate=2007-05-04 |access-date=2020-12-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

与英国许多的国家博物馆不同，它不是由公共资助，而是由慈善信托基金拥有和经营，因此需要入场费。

==打碎锁链 ==
爲纪念《1807年奴隶贸易法》废除[[大西洋奴隸貿易|大西洋奴隸貿易]]200周年，博物馆推出“打碎锁链”展览。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.artfundprize.org.uk/2008/shortlist1.php |title=The Art Fund Prize for museums and galleries – Press room |publisher=Artfundprize.org.uk |accessdate=2012-12-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120314184550/http://www.artfundprize.org.uk/2008/shortlist1.php |archivedate=2012-03-14 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

==关闭和争议==
2007年11月23日，博物馆宣布2008年将其核心业务搬到伦敦，<ref name="closure">{{cite web |url=http://www.empiremuseum.co.uk/aboutus/relationalnews.htm#move |title=News |accessdate=2007-03-13 |work=British Empire and Commonwealth Museum |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070401161447/http://www.empiremuseum.co.uk/aboutus/relationalnews.htm#move |archive-date=2007-04-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>该博物馆于2008年秋季不向公眾開放，<ref name="closure"/> 2009年3月底对学校关闭。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empiremuseum.co.uk/aboutus/aboutus.htm |title=About Us |publisher=British Empire & Commonwealth Museum |accessdate=2009-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090609041203/http://www.empiremuseum.co.uk/aboutus/aboutus.htm |archive-date=2009-06-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年3月16日，博物馆协会宣布，博物馆馆长加雷思·格里菲斯已解职，等待警方调查未经授权处置博物馆文物一案。<ref name="museumsassociation-20110316">{{cite web |url=http://www.museumsassociation.org/museums-journal/news/16032011-becm |title=Museum director dismissed pending police investigation |publisher=Museums Association |date=2011-03-16 |accessdate=2011-03-16 |archive-date=2017-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119164914/http://www.museumsassociation.org/museums-journal/news/16032011-becm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2011/mar/17/british-empire-museum-director-dismissed|title=Museum director leaves post amid police investigation into 'missing' exhibits|author=Steven Morris|work=The Guardian|date=2011-03-17|accessdate=2011-03-16|location=London|archive-date=2019-12-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191205064549/https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2011/mar/17/british-empire-museum-director-dismissed|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theartnewspaper.com/articles/Rise-and-fall-of-the-British-Empire-museum/24476|title=Rise and fall of the British Empire museum: As the scale of unethical disposals emerges, who knew what?|author=Gareth Harris|publisher=The Art Newspaper|date=2011-09-03|accessdate=2012-03-03|archive-date=2013-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105031655/http://www.theartnewspaper.com/articles/Rise-and-fall-of-the-British-Empire-museum/24476|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2012年3月28日，博物馆宣布取消搬迁到伦敦的计划<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empiremuseum.co.uk/ |title=British Empire and Commonwealth Museum |accessdate=2012-04-05 |work=British Empire and Commonwealth Museum |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110228112239/http://www.empiremuseum.co.uk/ |archivedate=2011-02-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，博物馆关闭后，这些藏品交给布里斯托市议会管理，由[[布里斯托尔城市博物馆与美术馆|布里斯托尔城市博物馆与美术馆]]展出。档案藏品（包括论文、书籍、摄影、电影和声音）由布里斯托档案馆保管。以前容纳博物馆的旧车站也给了市里，可能用于未来[[英國鐵路網公司|英國鐵路網公司]]去伦敦的业务<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bristol247.com/2012/03/29/empire-museum-collection-given-to-bristol-61388/ |title=Empire Museum collection given to Bristol |author=Editor |publisher=Bristol 24-7 |date=2012-03-29 |accessdate=2012-04-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105025304/http://www.bristol247.com/2012/03/29/empire-museum-collection-given-to-bristol-61388/ |archivedate=2013-11-05 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-17540037|title=Bristol museum could revert to rail platform|author=Editor|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|date=2012-03-28|accessdate=2012-04-05|archive-date=2012-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331114251/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-bristol-17540037|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年10月24日，大英帝国和英联邦博物馆和帝国博物馆有限公司進入「会员自愿清算」階段，由[[普华永道|普华永道]]的两名雇员擔任联合清算人。

